com.vmware.appliance.recovery.backup

Interface Schedules

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SchedulesTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SchedulesStub

    public interface Schedules
extends Service, SchedulesTypes
    The Schedules interface provides methods to be performed to manage backup schedules. This interface was added in vSphere API 6.7.
